      "id": "tutorial-monitoring-02",
      "markerIndex": 1,
      "replayStartSec": 8.503611,
      "replayEndSec": 14.799411,
      "narrationText": "现在查看容器。这个视图列出机器上每个仓库中所有运行中的容器，包括名称、状态、健康检查、CPU、内存，以及所属仓库。",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-monitoring/tutorial-monitoring-02.c69ddf28.mp3",
      "textHash": "c69ddf28ce631b3cecd0e08da1656e414116d3ba0f589494aafa4f5d5c2f281e",
      "audioDurationSec": 12.512653,
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-monitoring/tutorial-monitoring-02-after.8f5e9479.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 3.239184,
      "afterTextHash": "8f5e9479ee59d8fdc04a462b12a935c123667cae390cc2692beb76ea35156d30"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-monitoring-03",
      "markerIndex": 2,
      "replayStartSec": 14.799411,
      "replayEndSec": 21.195367,
      "narrationText": "然后是仓库本身。大小、挂载状态、Docker 守护进程状态、磁盘使用情况，机器上每个隔离环境的所有必要信息一览无余。",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-monitoring/tutorial-monitoring-03.849a5301.mp3",
      "textHash": "849a530101a5095af1efe3a77fef7e0ba608be392e6bb0df05c0042eb7e4a7f7",
      "audioDurationSec": 11.467755,
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-monitoring/tutorial-monitoring-03-after.dad9bf80.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 3.709388,
      "afterTextHash": "dad9bf8086ffa8e9d21f5016169e0e3ed15d5d8807ca62ff9d5cccc09e5ec4b3"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-monitoring-04",
      "markerIndex": 3,
      "replayStartSec": 21.195367,
      "replayEndSec": 26.969407,
      "narrationText": "机器查询命令一次性给你所有信息：系统信息、容器、仓库，全部汇聚在一起。运行一次即可得到完整全貌。",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-monitoring/tutorial-monitoring-04.8caa3f36.mp3",
      "textHash": "8caa3f360355edfd69962e9854a1f1bef8c5f69d60c13b0f0b4041714ab04974",
